title: Pairings Party Details Announced!
content: The 5th Annual International Cup Pairings Party will be held at Shutters on King in Leesburg, VA on October 16th from 6:30-9:30 PM. Food, drinks, and pairings revealed! Check out the [schedule](#schedule) for complete details including the menu.

title: International Cup 2025 dates set
content: The 2025 Lansdowne International Cup will be held from Oct.17 to Oct 18th. Check out the [tournament format](#format) and view the [complete schedule](#schedule) for more details.
